<i>for more happiness than this.</i>

32
00:03:51,481 --> 00:03:53,775
- Yes, that's good.
- Thank you.

33
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,653
<i>I would never get greedy</i>
<i>for any kind of fortune.</i>

34
