- Okay.
- Here.

45
00:04:29,018 --> 00:04:32,105
It's all cooked. Here I come!

46
00:04:32,188 --> 00:04:35,233
- I'm going to take it. Say cheese.
- Cheese!

47
00:04:35,316 --> 00:04:38,319
One, two, three!

48
00:04:38,403 --> 00:04:39,946
- Yay!
- It's cold!

49
