00:55:07,554 --> 00:55:09,139
<i>to the deceased and the family.</i>

641
00:55:09,222 --> 00:55:10,348
I'll see you next time.

642
00:55:10,432 --> 00:55:11,933
Come again.

643
00:55:20,108 --> 00:55:21,234
Let's go.

